The HomeDeviceSetup Diagnostics profile generates files that allow Apple to troubleshoot issues with your device and help Apple to improve its products and services. The generated files may contain some of your personal information, including information about your Home, devices in the Home, as well as Account Info related to the Home devices. The generated files will not otherwise contain any of the content of your Passes. The profile will expire after 3 days.
At all times, information received by Apple will be treated in accordance with Apple's Privacy Policy, which can be found at www.apple.com/privacy.
